snippet.title: Peaks of Yore - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2236070/Peaks_of_Yore/

Travel around The Great Gales to climb challenging peaks in this physics-based climbing adventure set in 1887.
Meet like-minded mountaineers, unlock helpful climbing gear, and become a pioneer of mountaineering.

Embark on an adventure to summit every boulder, peak, and mountain in The Great Gales.

https://www.peaksofyore.net/
